plot: This compilation includes the Award-Winning short films, "Terrence Baum: Intergalactic Assassin," "Agnes Keedan's Secret Plan," "Say Thankyou, Please," and "Evolution." Also included are satirical commercials for Twinkies snack cakes.
title: Puppets & Demons
